  "body": "### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Send an audio message in the chat.\r\n2. Record audio and leave it in the composer\r\n3. Attempt to play both the audio in the composer and the sent audio message in the chat.\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\n- Both the audio in the composer and the sent audio message can be played simultaneously.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/d56fddff-ca81-4cde-97b5-f7774d70afa7\r\n\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\n- When an audio message is played in the chat, the audio in the composer should be automatically paused to avoid simultaneous playback.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information:\r\n- Status version: [19 May 2023]\r\n",
